      <h3>
        What is our goal?
      </h3>
      <p>
        The City of Evanston would like to raise $25,000 in order to plant 100 new trees in parks and parkways throughout Evanston. We will plant a large variety of native species to improve our tree population's resiliency and support a larger diversity of flora and fauna. We want to be a model city to inspire other municipalities to invest in their own green infrastructure, and see the benefits of having cleaner air, reduced storm water run-off, higher property values, and safer neighborhoods.
      <p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

