      <h3>
        What will my donation do?
      </h3>
      <p>
       Every $250 represents a new tree. All of the revenue raised is going strictly towards the purchase of more trees to replace those that have died, and all donations are tax-deductible. With $25,000, we will be able to purchase at least 100 2.5-inch diameter trees from local nurseries. 
